channel.title: Concert Friday 6th March 2009
channel.description:
Last night (Friday 6th March 2009) i went to a concert. I saw Emarosa, The Spill Canvas and You Me At Six. Just thought i'd show you some vids which i have found from youtube :) Also i would like to say, i got the drummer of Emarosa's drum stick (snapped) and i touched the guitarists or drummers hand... he told me to let go :L
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gH0Rf8LYy58 - 0:00 - 1:40 = Emarosa, 1:42 + = You Me At Six's ultimate intro http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ysIzTlfwAtw&feature=related - Emarosa - The Past Should Stay Dead http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ssggbxY1OYI - You Me At Six - Jealous Minds Think Alike and Gossip Live in Bristol http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ptRUF8akKM - You Me At Six - Save it for the bedroom http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M0C1_MwCUu4 - Ending song
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EMIFG1Dfm44 - The first song is take off your colours and then is the truth is a terrible thing... at the end the song is meant to continue but they stoped and played fall out boy's sugar we're going down... WICKED XD
